  )
  
NamedSeries = RawSeries
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({_time:r._time, _value:r._value, _field: "TBT (Lighthouse v"+r.lighthouse_version+")"}))
  |> keep(columns:FinalOutput)

NamedSeries |> yield()
